Yep thats true Charm, and also hit the local libraries. Depending on the year it happened, old newspapers, obituaries, or books can usually hold info like that and if its something curious they may already have a folder of info if it pertains to local history on the hotel. A simple phone call to the libraries in the vicinity should give you an idea if they have any mircrofiche or digitally saved info from that era.


Misty


